Title: Multilingual PAL with Clint Huffman
Description: PAL is back, and speaking more languages! Richard chats with former PFE Clint Huffman about his latest work on Performance Analysis of Logs or PAL. For more than ten years, Clint has been supporting the open source project that helps you understand what's going on in all sorts of important Windows applications including Active Directory, SQL Server, BizTalk, Exchange Server and more. Clint talks about evolving PAL and it's sister tool CLU into Pro editions that you can subscribe to - stay tuned for more!
